    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's just an endless loop of trying to find meaning where there isn't any. it feels less like \"living\" and more like just... enduring. if the universe doesn't care and there's no objective point to the suffering, then why are we even expected to keep fighting it? it feels like we're just clinging to a sinking ship for no reason.",
